  "raw_html": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"msort\">\n<span id=\"api-paddle-msort\"></span>\n<h1>msort<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#msort\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\"></a></h1>\n<dl class=\"py function\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\">\n<span class=\"sig-prename descclassname\"><span class=\"pre\">paddle.</span></span>\n<span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">msort</span></span>\n<span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span>\n<em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">input</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Tensor</span></span></em>, \n         <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">*</span></span></em>, \n         <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">out</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Tensor</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">|</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></em>\n<span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span>\n<span class=\"sig-return\"><span class=\"sig-return-icon\">→</span> <span class=\"sig-return-typehint\"><span class=\"pre\">Tensor</span></span></span>\n<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/blob/release/3.3/python/paddle/tensor/search.py#L556\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a>\n</dt>\n<dd>\n<p>Sorts the input along the given axis = 0, and returns the sorted output tensor. The sort algorithm is ascending.</p>\n<dl class=\"field-list simple\">\n<dt class=\"field-odd\">\n           Parameters\n          </dt>\n<dd class=\"field-odd\">\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p>